dict.string: This is just a sample. Do NOT try loading it.
Ensure you understand EVERY field before booting.
In most cases recommended to use Sample.plist
Use SampleCustom.plist only for special cases.
change OSID to XSID (to avoid match against _OSI XOSI patch)
Sleep & Shutdown: _PTS to ZPTS(1,N) (copied from Daliansky's OC-Little)
Wake from Sleep: _WAK to ZWAK(1,N) (copied from Daliansky's OC-Little)
rename _STA methods in MATH and LDR2 device to XSTA
(I2C) rename Method(_STA,0,NS) in GPI0 to XSTA
(I2C) rename Method(_CRS,0,S) in ETPD to XCRS
